title: WHERE'S THE BAND TOUR IN STUDIO
description: The "Where's the Band Tour?" — which features lead singers from The Get Up Kids, Saves the Day, Bayside and more playing acoustic sets — has been traveling across the US the last few months and decided to make a pit stop at the Hurley Studio. Ant from Bayside, Chris from Saves the Day and Matt from Get Up Kids recorded their take on NOFX's "Linoleum". Enjoy!
